Day 94: Create VPC Using Terraform

Date: December 22, 2025
Overview
Provisioned AWS VPC infrastructure using Terraform.
Key Concepts Learned

Terraform basics
HCL syntax
Provider configuration
Resource blocks

Terraform Code
hclprovider "aws" {
  region = "us-east-1"
}

resource "aws_vpc" "main" {
  cidr_block           = "10.0.0.0/16"
  enable_dns_hostnames = true
  enable_dns_support   = true

  tags = {
    Name = "main-vpc"
    Environment = "production"
  }
}

resource "aws_subnet" "public" {
  vpc_id            = aws_vpc.main.id
  cidr_block        = "10.0.1.0/24"
  availability_zone = "us-east-1a"

  tags = {
    Name = "public-subnet"
  }
}
Commands Used
bashterraform init
terraform plan
terraform apply
terraform destroy
Challenges Faced
Understanding Terraform state and dealing with AWS IAM permissions.
